#: src/Form/TemplateContributeFieldset.php:48
msgid ""
"In complex workflow, the template for the user may be different from the "
"template of the item, for example to create a form with different property "
"labels, or a different order, or more restrictive rules of property "
"validation, or different templates for different users. So this option "
"changes the template when the contribution is validated."
